{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Turn-based competition is an exciting capability added in Game Center for iOS 5. Learn about the new API and user interface for turn-based play and see how it applies in a variety of popular game genres. Gain insight into managing turn-based game state and get details about how the turn is passed from player to player."}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-412-turnbased-gaming-with-game-center"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode","title":"Turn-Based Gaming with Game Center","roleHeading":"WWDC11"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-412-TurnBased-Gaming-with-Game-Center"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/412\/","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"}},"references":{"WWDC11.jpeg":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC11.jpeg"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Learn More…","ty